# Git and versioning

- Work on **`develop`**; branch `feature/*`, `fix/*`, or `chore/*` from there
- **`main`** receives tagged releases only (`vX.Y.Z` annotated tags on merge)
- SemVer in `package.json`; bump via `npm run version:patch|minor|major`
- `CHANGELOG.md` follows [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/) — `[Unreleased]` on `develop`
- Conventional Commits: `feat:`, `fix:`, `chore:`, `docs:`, `refactor:`, `sync:`

Full workflow: `docs/git-workflow-and-versioning.md`

## Commits and pushes

- Only commit when the user explicitly asks
- Never force-push to `main`/`master`
- Never skip hooks unless the user requests it
- Never commit `.env`, `*.db`, `sharepoint-config.json`, or secrets
- Ask before any `git push` or branch operations beyond local commits

## Release checklist

1. Merge `develop` → `main`
2. `npm run version:patch` (or minor/major) on `main`
3. `git tag -a vX.Y.Z -m "vX.Y.Z"`
4. Push `main` and tags: `git push origin main --tags`
5. Build tablet package: `npm run build`
